abstract = {Feel the shape, texture, and motion of virtual objects. 130 points of feedback displace your skin up to 2mm, with no perceivable latency. Feel size, weight, and impact in virtual reality. A lightweight exoskeleton applies up to 4 lbs. of resistive force feedback per finger. Manipulate your hands with unparalleled accuracy. Integrated motion capture allows for occlusion-free interaction, tracking 6 degrees of freedom per digit with sub-millimeter precision. With plugins for Unity, Unreal Engine 4, and a low-level C++ API, the HaptX SDK makes it easy to develop new content or upgrade existing VR experiences for HaptX Gloves.},
