title = {Accessible Apps creates high quality accessible software for the blind.},
url = {https://q-continuum.net/},
abstract = {We make useful, innovative software, the kind blind people hope someone will make but can't really find anywhere else. Why do we say this? Our development team is made up of blind people who have many of the same needs. We write software because we need to do something, and we can't find an accessible way to do it. Our mission is to create software that improves the computing experience for blind and visually impaired people. We're committed to innovation, and accessible, affordable software. Check out our apps from the software menu. We offer demos for all programs and extremely reasonable prices for a range of powerful applications that you'll find yourself using every day.},
