abstract={Amazingly, people sometimes prefer software systems that hinder their ability to use them.},
annotation={This paper may explain why sighted people prefer visual maps over audio maps. There are many factors that go into prefference, and performance is not always the most important. It could be the color, asthentics, familiarity, or preconseptions.},
